                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Peel-and-stick the included Tenacious Tape Mini Patches (1.5” x 2”) to repair a hole in puff jackets and sleeping bags; includes six washable and waterproof patches",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Spray on the Revivex Durable Water Repellent (10.5 oz) to add water repellency to down jackets and sleeping bags all season long",
