        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Wash, protect and fix down jackets, sleeping bags, and other down-filled gear with the Revivex Down Care Kit. This essential kit includes the gentle Revivex Down Cleaner soap, which restores loft without stripping natural oils, and six Tenacious Tape Mini Patches (3 clear and 3 black nylon). The washable, peel-and-stick patches are easy to apply and ideal for covering up burn holes or rips and tears on the go. For a total down care system, select the kit with Revivex Durable Water Repellent (DWR) to keep gear and the body dry. Stay warm and comfortable outdoors with the Revivex Down Care Kit.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
